# Green-Sprout-Cafe

## Overview
This project is a web application designed to facilitate online food ordering and delivery for a cafe.

## Features
- Browse menu
- Place orders
- Track delivery status

## Setup
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/mxlimmm28s/Green-Sprout-Cafe.git

   cd green-sprout-cafe
   npm install

   git add .
